{"TopicId":198821,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Switching engines in flight?","CreatedByName":"strider3","CreatedById":199830,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-18T19:40:07Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"strider3","CreatedById":199830,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-18T19:40:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have been struggling to build a craft that can land on Laythe (see below). \u0022Verticals\u0022 require too much fuel/oxidizer weight so I\u0027m trying to take advantage of an air breathing engine to get me closer to orbit. Below is a picture of a modified stock \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vertical Take-Off and Landing\u0022\u003EVTOL\u003C/abbr\u003E I\u0027m playing with (it\u0027s nowhere near done yet, so be kind \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E). My thought is to use the Twitches to get a vertical rise off the surface, then the Wheesley to fly forward (there will be wings and rudders, eventually) and the Terriers to get into orbit and dock. My first question is how do you swap between the Twitches to the Wheesley...then to the Terriers? I have no idea how that can be accomplished. How do you shut down 12 Twitches (12 might be overkill, at this point)? I currently have to click each one and shut it down individually so that my throttle only controls the Wheesley...by that time I\u0027ll be crashed, me thinks? The problem I always run into, in any multiple engine construction, is how to enable, disable or \u0022throttle limit\u0022 all of an engine group at once (that is an issue I have with any craft...not just this one).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m sure I\u0027ll run into other problems going forward...but for now...how does one go about switching engines, and their throttle controls, in flight?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://users.frii.com/viciii3/screenshot1.jpg\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 style=\u0022height:auto;\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 alt=\u0022screenshot1.jpg\u0022 src=\u0022http://users.frii.com/viciii3/screenshot1.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fraktal","CreatedById":184990,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-18T19:46:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdd the engines\u0027 toggle action to an action group in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E. You can then use the 1-9 keys to switch them on or off.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"antipro","CreatedById":173370,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-18T19:48:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223895594\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198821\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221608320407\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022199830\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022strider3\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, strider3 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do you shut down 12 Twitches?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\naction group doesn\u0027t work?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"strider3","CreatedById":199830,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-18T19:50:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223895598\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198821\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221608320809\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184990\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Fraktal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, Fraktal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdd the engines\u0027 toggle action to an action group in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E. You can then use the 1-9 keys to switch them on or off.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOK, I\u0027ll try...action groups have been...hard for me to understand, exactly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223895601\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198821\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221608320900\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022173370\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022antipro\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, antipro said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\naction group doesn\u0027t work?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSee above...LOL!\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, I have no idea how to use action groups. Anybody know of a detailed tutorial on that?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fraktal","CreatedById":184990,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-18T19:55:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s not that hard. Any action you put into a numbered\u00A0action group (you need level 3 \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E/\u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003ESPH\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E) is executed each time you tap the corresponding number key on your keyboard.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor example, all of my aircraft have the 1 key as an engine master switch. On my first interplanetary craft, I set both the orbiter and the lander to toggle their engines with the 1 key, then light up the orbiter\u0027s engine via stating, so that the key now alternate\u00A0between the two sets of engines. Back when I built my first \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E, I had an action group toggle between the main engines and the Puff \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vertical Take-Off and Landing\u0022\u003EVTOL\u003C/abbr\u003E engines.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-12-18T19:56:58Z\u0022 title=\u002212/18/2020 07:56  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 18, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Fraktal\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"strider3","CreatedById":199830,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-18T20:01:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/184990-fraktal/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022184990\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/184990-fraktal/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Fraktal\u003C/a\u003E Thanks, but...I\u0027m going to need way more detail on the \u0022how to\u0022 on action groups. More of a step-by-step thing...\u0022Click this, enter that, select this\u0022. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"antipro","CreatedById":173370,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-18T20:11:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223895607\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198821\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221608321675\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022199830\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022strider3\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 minutes ago, strider3 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMore of a step-by-step thing...\u0022Click this, enter that, select this\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022action%20group%20sbs.jpg?dl=1\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/mop8ffid4brqzpj/action%20group%20sbs.jpg?dl=1\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nResult:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022action%20group%20result.jpg?dl=1\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002285.34\u0022 height=\u0022425\u0022 width=\u0022498\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/53nryoe02tsk3si/action%20group%20result.jpg?dl=1\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"strider3","CreatedById":199830,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-18T20:13:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd the key to use would be the \u00224\u0022 key? How do I select all my Twitches? In my screenshot you can see they are in batches of two\u0027s?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-12-18T20:15:37Z\u0022 title=\u002212/18/2020 08:15  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 18, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by strider3\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"antipro","CreatedById":173370,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-18T20:15:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223895613\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198821\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221608322418\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022199830\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022strider3\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, strider3 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd the key to use would be the \u00224\u0022 key?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyes, in this case I choosed the \u00224\u0022 key as an example, you can use from 0 to 9\u003Cbr\u003E\nand you can add more actions, like other parts/actions with the same key.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-12-18T20:18:26Z\u0022 title=\u002212/18/2020 08:18  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 18, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by antipro\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"strider3","CreatedById":199830,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-18T20:22:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust to make sure I\u0027m thinking correctly...in the situation above I would have 3 keys, one each to \u0022toggle\u0022 each engine group (Twitches - 1, Wheesley - 2 and Terriers - 3). To swap from Twitches to Wheesley I would hit key \u00221\u0022 then \u00222\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fraktal","CreatedById":184990,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-18T20:28:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223895613\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198821\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221608322418\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022199830\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022strider3\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 minutes ago, strider3 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do I select all my Twitches? In my screenshot you can see they are in batches of two\u0027s?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you added the parts to your vessel via symmetry, the action group will apply to all parts in the symmetry. In other words, you only need to add each Twitch pair once.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223895619\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198821\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221608322921\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022199830\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022strider3\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, strider3 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo swap from Twitches to Wheesley I would hit key \u00221\u0022 then \u00222\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nExactly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"antipro","CreatedById":173370,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-18T20:28:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223895619\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198821\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221608322921\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022199830\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022strider3\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, strider3 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI would have 3 keys, one each to \u0022toggle\u0022 each engine group (Twitches - 1, Wheesley - 2 and Terriers - 3). To swap from Twitches to Wheesley I would hit key \u00221\u0022 then \u00222\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ncorrect, or also you can bind the \u0022toggle\u0022 action for both Twitches and Wheesley with the same key.\u003Cbr\u003E\nso, with one key pression you turn on one engines set and turn off the other set.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-12-18T20:29:38Z\u0022 title=\u002212/18/2020 08:29  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 18, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by antipro\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"strider3","CreatedById":199830,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-18T20:28:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYears of KSP...and not knowing Action groups...sheesh!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks antipro! I see a lot of new abilities now!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-12-18T20:30:32Z\u0022 title=\u002212/18/2020 08:30  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 18, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by strider3\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"antipro","CreatedById":173370,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-18T20:39:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223895625\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198821\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221608323324\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022199830\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022strider3\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, strider3 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYears of KSP...and not knowing Action groups...sheesh!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have about 4k hours of play but still don\u0027t know a lot of things, ...it\u0027s rocket science.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223895625\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198821\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221608323324\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022199830\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022strider3\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 minutes ago, strider3 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks antipro! I see a lot of new abilities now!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyou\u0027re welcome\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"antipro","CreatedById":173370,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-12-18T20:57:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/199830-strider3/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022199830\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/199830-strider3/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@strider3\u003C/a\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EI forgot to mention that you can edit the \u0022action groups\u0022 even while in flight\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022action%20groups%20in%20flight.jpg?dl=1\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002262.67\u0022 height=\u0022470\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/j4llt2rw5dxqaca/action%20groups%20in%20flight.jpg?dl=1\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}